{"tid":742192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上批評習近平 呂千榮「被患」精神病","createTime":"2018-07-14T10:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T12:26:32.000Z","uid":70063,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6433e84a60648f31a2012420fda200ae32ef173f","tid":742192,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:42:07.000Z","msg":"中國安徽異見人士呂千榮，經常在網上批判中國政府和習近平，被中共當局勸說到醫院檢查是否「精神有問題」。<br />\n<br />\n據《自由亞洲電台》報導，呂千榮在九十年代，就因具名舉報地方政府的貪腐行為，被判處三年勞教，迄今二十多年，仍然受中共注意。安徽霍邱縣近日派地方官員「探訪」呂千榮，希望出錢替他檢查有否「精神有問題」。<br />\n<br />\n呂千榮說，他「被」罹患精神病，因為自己在網上痛批習近平，而有官員告誡他不要說「不該說的話」。可是呂千榮認為，他身為中國公民，就有監督中國政府的責任和義務。<br />\n<br />\n官員無法說服呂千榮「看病」，便轉移目標至呂千榮的太太，直說他是精神病患者，可能會把妻子殺害，藉此要求呂妻把丈夫送往醫院治療，甚至希望她和呂千榮離婚。<br />\n<br />\n北京維權人士王荔蕻表示，「被」罹患精神病是中國政府壓迫異見人士的常見手段。因送到精神病院後，無需拘留或審判等法律程序，便可對維權人士為所欲為，任意殘害他們身心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/2018/07/13/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E5%91%82%E5%8D%83%E6%A6%AE%E3%80%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%82%A3%E3%80%8D%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E5%2591%2582%25E5%258D%2583%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2582%25A3%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%2597%2585%2F&d=Id4rIygsUOkloCAncYl3ydr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bba955d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://maddog.myradio.hk/2018/07/13/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E5%91%82%E5%8D%83%E6%A6%AE%E3%80%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%82%A3%E3%80%8D%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85/</a>"},{"pid":"7b0d05748d315c2ab1f497a24042ff6f9b01e63f","tid":742192,"uid":170383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9f95cf1f77e70cca9288b3f5f20517a5cbb932","tid":742192,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b0d05748d315c2ab1f497a24042ff6f9b01e63f","tid":742192,"uid":170383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ecaed69d9da6fc245b598fccbc8ae53adcfc04","tid":742192,"uid":134323,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"某程度上，係大陸夠膽開名出 post 屌習種都算係痴線"},{"pid":"8da47ae14bd1f67efb97bc0e399882d12e0a70fc","tid":742192,"uid":53705,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"66ecaed69d9da6fc245b598fccbc8ae53adcfc04","tid":742192,"uid":134323,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"某程度上，係大陸夠膽開名出 post 屌習種都算係痴線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:13:52.000Z","msg":"係大陸做一個有良知既人,   已經係精神唔正常"},{"pid":"c08c19ec6c1cc0a7234f42027778956967caf816","tid":742192,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:17:00.000Z","msg":"烈士, 值得尊敬"},{"pid":"0a678b3929b0943e382f1e8f2717bce9c37cc843","tid":742192,"uid":142658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:47:18.000Z","msg":"某程度上佢真係有 佢咁做同自殺有咩分別"},{"pid":"ab6daa03d454896647d608c6ed567866bd07debf","tid":742192,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T12:26:32.000Z","msg":"周星馳俾人話係痴線 因佢乜都唔驚"}]}